death and must have:
(A) received a discharge from the armed forces of the United
States under conditions other than conditions set forth in
IC 10-17-12-7.5(2); IC 10-17-12-8.1(2); or
(B) died while serving in the armed forces of the United
States; or
(2) the decedent must have been the spouse or surviving spouse
of a person described in subdivision (1)(A) or (1)(B) and must
