described in subdivision (1).
(4) Was discharged from the armed forces of the United States
under conditions other than conditions set forth in
IC 10-17-12-7.5(2). IC 10-17-12-8.1(2).
SECTION 70. IC 20-20-7-7, AS AMENDED BY P.L.238-2025,
